On the final day of this year's Spirit Week, the freshmen, sophomores and juniors decked out in white and green while the seniors wore camo. The lunch rally, held outside in the rain, included pumpkin bowling and a staff dance. Check back to The Paly Voice for more Spirit Week coverage.

